

	This directory contains the sources for the NOAO Data Transport System (DTS).
Files in this directory include:

    README	This file
    bin		Application binaries 
    bits	Save-The-Bits sources.  To be used in development of ingest tools
    doc		System documentation
    etc		Sample files for installing DTS as a unix service
    include	Source include files
    lib		DTS libraries
    libdts	Main DTS interface library
    libxrpc	XMLRPC-C wrapper library providing simplified interface
    src		Application sources
    tests	Test / dummy programs
    web		Experimental web interface 
